abstract: Stock market reacts negatively to mixed earnings reports from companies and logs its first day of losses for the week, but stocks end with first weekly gain of 2015.
lead_paragraph: Kimberly-Clark and UPS disappointed while Starbucks’s earnings soared, but over all investors seem to be tempering expectations.

headline.main: A Mixed Bag of Earnings Weighs on the Market
